f10FpStatsMib.name: f10FpStatsMib

revisions.description: Added fpCpuDataPlaneCOSTable for Rx and Tx COS queues in CPU data plane.

f10FpStatsMib.description: Dell Networking OS forward plane statistics mib.

fpCpuDataPlaneTable.name: fpCpuDataPlaneTable
fpCpuDataPlaneTable.description: The data plane statistics table contains the data plane statistics of a stack unit/line card which includes the received, dropped statistics and per COS transmission and reception statistics . In case of multi CPU platforms, this table contains the data plane statistics for each cpu. The table index will represent the CPUs in order as {CP cpus, RP cpus, LP cpus}.

fpStackUnitIndex.name: fpStackUnitIndex
fpStackUnitIndex.description: Stack unit number or line card number.

fpRxError.name: fpRxError
fpRxError.description: Gives statistics about the reception error

fpRxDatapathError.name: fpRxDatapathError
fpRxDatapathError.description: Statistics of reception data path error.

fpTxDatapathErr.name: fpTxDatapathErr
fpTxDatapathErr.description: Data path error in transmitted data.

fpCpuPartyBusTable.name: fpCpuPartyBusTable
fpCpuPartyBusTable.description: The party bus statistics table contains statistics about the number of input and output packets, bytes, error and the number of input packets dropped in a stack unit/line card.

fpDropsTable.name: fpDropsTable
fpDropsTable.description: The forwarding plane drops table contains the list of various drops per port in a stack unit/line card.

fpIngIBPCBPFullDrops.name: fpIngIBPCBPFullDrops
fpIngIBPCBPFullDrops.description: The number of packets discarded because of Ingress Back Pressure (flow control), or because the Common Buffer Pool is full.

fpIngPortSTPnotFwdDrops.name: fpIngPortSTPnotFwdDrops
fpIngPortSTPnotFwdDrops.description: Packets dropped due to Spanning Tree State not in forwarding state.

fpIngPolicyDiscards.name: fpIngPolicyDiscards
fpIngPolicyDiscards.description: Packet dropped due to policy discards.

fpPacketBufferTable.name: fpPacketBufferTable
fpPacketBufferTable.description: The packet buffer table contains the modular packet buffers details per stack unit/line card and the mode of allocation.

fpPacketBufferEntry.name: fpPacketBufferEntry
fpPacketBufferEntry.description: Packet buffer details per stack unit/line card.

fpPortPipe.name: fpPortPipe
fpPortPipe.description: fpPortPipe denotes the portpipe in the stack unit/line card.

fpStatsPerPortTable.name: fpStatsPerPortTable
fpStatsPerPortTable.description: The forward plane stats per port table contains the packet buffer usage per port per stack unit/line card.

fpStatsPerPortEntry.name: fpStatsPerPortEntry
fpStatsPerPortEntry.description: Per port stats and per COS stats.

fpStatsPerCOSTable.name: fpStatsPerCOSTable
fpStatsPerCOSTable.description: The forwarding plane statistics per COS table gives packet buffer statistics per COS per port.

fpCpuPartyBusPortStatsTable.description: The party bus port statistics table contains statistics about the number of input and output packets, bytes, error and the number of input packets dropped in a party bus port. This table is applicable to platforms which support party bus statistics at per port level.
